SELECT [i].[InternshipApplicationId], [i].[ApplicationDate], [i].[ApplicationStatus], [i].[DegreeProgram], [i].[InternshipId], [i].[LinkedInProfile], [i].[Resume], [i].[UniversityName], [i].[UserId], [u].[UserId], [u].[Email], [u].[MobileNumber], [u].[Password], [u].[SecretKey], [u].[UserRole], [u].[Username], [i0].[InternshipId], [i0].[ApplicationDeadline], [i0].[CompanyName], [i0].[Description], [i0].[DurationInMonths], [i0].[Location], [i0].[SkillsRequired], [i0].[Stipend], [i0].[Title]
FROM [InternshipApplications] AS [i]
